              From: Univariate Polynomial Ring in a over Rational Field
              To:   Univariate Polynomial Ring in a over Rational Field
              Defn:   Ring morphism:
                      From: Univariate Polynomial Ring in a over Rational Field
                      To:   Univariate Polynomial Ring in x over Rational Field
                      Defn: a |--> 2*x
